<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA625_05_IH_0002</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema625_05.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_05_ih_0002 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="2_light_purple" lang="y">
					모눈을 이용하여 반지름이 6 ㎝인 원의 넓이를 어림하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">초록색 선 안쪽 모눈은 모두 몇 칸이고, 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구해 보세요.</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
							<p>1 ㎠</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<div class="flex align_center">
								<span lang="y">모눈 :</span>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="88"></math-field>
								</div>
								<span lang="y">칸</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex align_center">
								<span lang="y">넓이 :</span>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="88"></math-field>
								</div>
								<span lang="y">㎠</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">
										원을 4등분한 것에서 초록색 선 안쪽 모눈 칸 수를 세어 보면 22칸이므로 초록색 선
										안쪽 모눈 칸 수는 모두 22×4=88(칸)입니다. 따라서 넓이는 88 ㎠입니다.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">빨간색 선 안쪽 모눈은 모두 몇 칸이고, 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구해 보세요.</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
							<p>1 ㎠</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<div class="flex align_center">
								<span lang="y">모눈 :</span>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="132"></math-field>
								</div>
								<span lang="y">칸</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex align_center">
								<span lang="y">넓이 :</span>
								<div class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="132"></math-field>
								</div>
								<span lang="y">㎠</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">
										원을 4등분한 것에서 빨간색 선 안쪽 모눈 칸 수를 세어 보면 33칸이므로 빨간색 선
										안쪽 모눈 칸 수는 모두 33×4=132(칸)입니다. 따라서 넓이는 132㎠입니다.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="page page_3">
					<h3 class="title" lang="y">원의 넓이를 어림해 보세요.</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
							<p>1 ㎠</p>
						</div>
						<div class="input_area">
							<div class="img_area">
								<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA625_05_IH/0002_02.png" alt="" />
								<div>
									<div class="flex align_center input_row">
										<span lang="y">원의 넓이는</span>
										<div class="input_wrap ml_10">
											<math-field data-answer-single="88"></math-field>
										</div>
										<span lang="y">㎠보다 넓고</span>
									</div>
									<div class="flex align_center input_row">
										<div class="input_wrap">
											<math-field data-answer-single="132"></math-field>
										</div>
										<span lang="y">㎠보다 좁습니다.</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p lang="y">반지름이 6 ㎝인 원의 넓이는 88 ㎠보다 넓고 132 ㎠보다 좁습니다</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
